      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASUAL ESCAPE (1) took the sit on the lead but levelled up to score (20.08) at this track in a Grade 5 over 340m. Great chance to get the job done again. LONG DARK ROAD (8) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (25.23) at this track. Has never been out of the money in three starts this course and distance. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expecting another good run. FANTASTIC ELLE (2) was well supported last start but didn't deliver when seventh (25.86), beaten 6 lengths. Finished third the start before. The form out of her last race has been franked. Key runner on best form. LITTLE MIMI (7) comes back from a let-up as a top three prospect.",
